document.discussion_title: Students visit Air Force Station Hakimpet on the eve of Independence Day
document.topic_text: Home / Photos / Hyderabad / Students visit Air Force Station Hakimpet on the eve of Independence Day Students visit Air Force Station Hakimpet on the eve of Independence Day August 12, 2016 Hyderabad , Photos Leave a comment HYDERABAD, AUG 11 (UNI)- School children visiting an exhibition of Indian Air Force as part of 70th Independence Day celebration, at Hakimpet Air Force Station in Hyderabad on Thursday. UNI PHOTO-90U HYDERABAD, AUG 11 (UNI)- People visiting a an exhibition as part of 70th Independence Day celebration, at Hakimpet Air Force Station in Hyderabad on Thursday. UNI PHOTO-91U HYDERABAD, AUG 11 (UNI)- School children visiting an exhibition of Indian Air Force as part of 70th Independence Day celebration, at Hakimpet Air Force Station in Hyderabad on Thursday. UNI PHOTO-90U HYDERABAD, AUG 11 (UNI)- Two Hawk trainer aircrafts taking off during a show as part of 70th Independence Day celebration, at Hakimpet Air Force Station in Hyderabad on Thursday. UNI PHOTO-89U School children visiting an exhibition of Indian Air Force as part of 70th Independence Day celebration, at Hakimpet Air Force Station in Hyderabad on Thursday. UNI PHOTO 2016-08-12
